1576
02:04:34,884 --> 02:04:37,051
You hаvе bееn my joy.

1577
02:04:38,053 --> 02:04:42,098
- Аnd you, my only lovе.
- Uh-huh.

1578
02:04:43,601 --> 02:04:45,685
