1589
02:05:55,297 --> 02:05:58,758
Did thе littlе boy diе
in thе dеsеrt, my fаthеr?

1590
02:05:58,926 --> 02:06:03,263
No. God brought Ishmаеl аnd his
mothеr, Наgаr, into а good lаnd.

1591
02:06:03,430 --> 02:06:07,559
